<p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #fff;font-size: 14px">Sanchit is a tech-enthusiast, reverse engineer and a software developer. He maintains a <a href="http://www.sanchitkarve.com/blog" style="color: #fff">Blog</a> and is a forum moderator on <a href="http://www.dreamincode.net" style="color: #fff">Dream.In.Code</a>, a programming and web-development community with over 470,000 members. He has an ardent interest in Mobile Phone Development, Web Development and Reverse Engineering.</p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #fff;font-size: 14px">He currently works at McAfee, Inc. as an Anti-Malware Researcher near Portland, Oregon where he spends his spare time biking/hiking to explore Oregon's diverse natural beauty.</p>
<p style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #fff;font-size: 14px">You can see some of his <a href="http://www.sanchitkarve.com/projects" style="color: #fff">projects</a>, view his <a href="http://www.sanchitkarve.com/resume/sanchitkarve_resume.pdf" style="color: #fff">r&eacute;sum&eacute;</a> (<a href="http://www.sanchitkarve.com/resume/sanchitkarve_resume_tldr.pdf" style="color: #fff">TLDR version</a>) or find him on these networks.</p>
